race.comment: The $3 million Sunlight 3YO Plate. GRAFTERBURNERS (2) hasn't put a hoof wrong this campaign stringing three wins together on the bounce and is racing in a rich vein of form. Boasts a win around this circuit, draws low and gets gun jock McDonald in the saddle. Plenty to like about his prospects. ICE KOOL (5) has put back-to-back wins together to start the career and looks to have a bunch of upside. Can bring up the hat-trick here. AKAYSHA (7) is yet to miss the top-four in seven career efforts and has tuned up for this with a recent trial placing. Draws the inside marble and shouldn't be underestimated. SAVVY HALLIE (6) is a G2 winner who is yet to run a bad race in seven outings. Has to be included. The well-related SWORDPLAY (9) (full to 4xG3 winner and G2 placed Recommendation) best of the rest in a cracking contest.
